  "notes_2026_05_21_revision": "family classifier fixed: previously matched bare \"fill\" which false-matched \"prefill\" and mis-classified two awq_fusedw4_prefill_* kernels as runtime_memset.  Re-classified as w4_dual_prefill_smallbatch (60 calls/pass, 7.4 ms) and w4_single_prefill_smallbatch (60 calls/pass, 3.6 ms).  These are QKV / shared-expert / dense-MLP fp16 fused-W4 prefill kernels that fire because dispatch is gated . At tokens=4 (verifier B=3) the prefill kernel is suboptimal vs the GEMV path that MoE selected experts use."
